/// VESTIGIAL source 'By source' (caption 'Country & Regions', 5,496 rows) - NO worksheet in the workbook binds it (verified). Modelled for source-fidelity per the explicit 5-table requirement; safe to omit if trimming. Same FNR kWh columns plus Region/Income group.
